  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/24629992" />
    <a title="laaaaames" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/178320-laaaaames"><img alt="laaaaames" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1282004147p2/178320.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/24629992?book_show_action=true">Jun 16, 2008</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="laaaaames" class="user" itemprop="url" name="laaaaames" href="/user/show/178320-laaaaames">laaaaames</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer24629992" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18028889487168265018">This book is really important, considering:<br/><br/>1. We are likely not safe from another random crazy deadly virus that will catch us offguard.<br/><br/>2. You have probably underestimated what an asshole Reagan was.<br/><br/>3. You might be going to see <i>Milk</i> soon and would like to read of some of what happened after him in SF politics.<br/><br/>4. Prop 8 effing passed, proving our society has farther to come than perhaps we realized.<br/><br/>Points deducted because apparently the Patient Zero story is a bit hinky. Also it&apos;s often a lot to </span>
  <span id="freeText18028889487168265018" style="display:none">This book is really important, considering:<br /><br />1. We are likely not safe from another random crazy deadly virus that will catch us offguard.<br /><br />2. You have probably underestimated what an asshole Reagan was.<br /><br />3. You might be going to see <i>Milk</i> soon and would like to read of some of what happened after him in SF politics.<br /><br />4. Prop 8 effing passed, proving our society has farther to come than perhaps we realized.<br /><br />Points deducted because apparently the Patient Zero story is a bit hinky. Also it's often a lot to keep plodding through it. Still worthwhile, especially as a historical document.</span>
