<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer1486631980292348822">Randy Shilts was a highly acclaimed, pioneering gay American journalist and author. He worked as a reporter for both <i>The Advocate</i> and the <i>San Francisco Chronicle</i>, as well as for San Francisco Bay Area television stations.</span>

</div>
